Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity

Class ProjectEntity

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity.ProjectEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class ProjectEntity extends Object implements Serializable
The ProjectEntity class represents the "project" table in the database. Each instance of this class corresponds to a single row in the table.
